normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"你睇下個垃圾政府 再諗諗你自己呢條問題<br />\n<br />\n大家就諗到啲公墓員咩質素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"所以我嘅結論就係喺廢港最梗要「錢」同「人脈」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用「錢」換「成功」可以向洗米華個仔學習<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20170602/s00016/1496339528228/洗米華大仔周柏豪榮升ceo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20170602%2Fs00016%2F1496339528228%2F%E6%B4%97%E7%B1%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%94%E5%91%A8%E6%9F%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%A6%AE%E5%8D%87ceo&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=5151ab9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20170602%2Fs00016%2F1496339528228%2F%E6%B4%97%E7%B1%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%94%E5%91%A8%E6%9F%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%A6%AE%E5%8D%87ceo&h=0c843b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20170602/s00016/1496339528228/洗米華大仔周柏豪榮升ceo</a><br />\n<br />\n用「人脈」換「成功」可以向星之屎學習<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/135545/28歲仔打理30人公司-陳易希評-星之子-光環-方便搲水吹\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F135545%2F28%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E6%89%93%E7%90%8630%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E9%99%B3%E6%98%93%E5%B8%8C%E8%A9%95-%E6%98%9F%E4%B9%8B%E5%AD%90-%E5%85%89%E7%92%B0-%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E6%90%B2%E6%B0%B4%E5%90%B9&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=57f98b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/135545/28歲仔打理30人公司-陳易希評-星之子-光環-方便搲水吹</a><br />\n<br />\n喺廢港要成功得𠵱兩條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"但無論用「錢」、「人脈」換「成功」，都需要學一招，叫「糖衣包屎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係將一個係人都諗到嘅垃圾 idea，連埋你嘅「錢」、「人脈」嘅資源，包成粒糖，再不斷發大嚟搞，好似一個龐氏騙局咁，唔理三七廿一，總之有咁大吹咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【例子】<br />\n<br />\nIdea：搵乜搵柒 =&gt; 就搵醫生啦 App<br />\n<br />\n包裝：<br />\n- 摘星之子名銜<br />\n- 某某大企業人脈贊助<br />\n- 政府葉劉人脈呃埋 funding<br />\n- 互聯網+ 吹水概念<br />\n<br />\n再用筆錢請班 IT 狗做，做完炒撚晒大部分，留返一兩隻狗去 maintain<br />\n<br />\n再包裝：<br />\n- 人工智能（出面啲人鬼知你乜叫 AI 咩）<br />\n- chatbot<br />\n- video conference API<br />\n- 再利用人脈吹大啲<br />\n<br />\n咁就進化為「超級搵醫生啦 App」，可以搞 IPO，發行 stock option 再不斷 buy back cap 水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdea80acc332bc86b1cabbd21bee616c27f550fb","tid":1824132,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279b46ab409fddf3682049f909ecdb3e7a02a6fe","tid":1824132,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e2fd4f0413d3885241af878bbd2b70c3e61d76","tid":1824132,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63401752e593e1be5dd6ceeb08e650bd381b422","tid":1824132,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"你睇下個垃圾政府 再諗諗你自己呢條問題<br />\n<br />\n大家就諗到啲公墓員咩質素"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"所以我嘅結論就係喺廢港最梗要「錢」同「人脈」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用「錢」換「成功」可以向洗米華個仔學習<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20170602/s00016/1496339528228/洗米華大仔周柏豪榮升ceo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20170602%2Fs00016%2F1496339528228%2F%E6%B4%97%E7%B1%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%94%E5%91%A8%E6%9F%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%A6%AE%E5%8D%87ceo&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=5151ab9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20170602%2Fs00016%2F1496339528228%2F%E6%B4%97%E7%B1%B3%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%94%E5%91%A8%E6%9F%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%A6%AE%E5%8D%87ceo&h=0c843b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20170602/s00016/1496339528228/洗米華大仔周柏豪榮升ceo</a><br />\n<br />\n用「人脈」換「成功」可以向星之屎學習<